\@writefile{tdo}{\contentsline {todo}{\fcolorbox {black}{blue!20}{\textcolor {blue!20}{o}}\ Baldo: Excellent extraction of my core claim. Yes, the transition from epistemic to ontic is the crux of my V3 argument.}{2}{section*.1}\protected@file@percent }
